The paper presents a machine learning method for distance metric learning, which is a common topic in the subfield of machine learning known as "Learning Theory" (cs.LG). The method is applied to classification tasks, which are often studied in computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method also involves kernel-based techniques, which are commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.NE.
